    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 20th level, you gain the ability to harness extraordinary martial prowess. As an action, you can magically become an avatar of conquest, gaining the following benefits for 1 minute:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You have resistance to all damage.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When you take the @action[Attack] action on your turn, you can make one additional attack as part of that action.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Your melee weapon attacks score a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20 on the [[/r d20]].</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
